## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a54a0-102">Экземпляр <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> создается, когда <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> объекта вызывает <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> событий.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a54a0-102">An instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> is created when the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object raises the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a54a0-103">Чтобы получить сведения о результате распознавания, доступ к <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> свойство в обработчике для события.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a54a0-103">To obtain information about the result of recognition, access the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property in the handler for the event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a54a0-104">Эмуляция — это процесс, с помощью которого текста вместо аудио, являются входными данными для механизма распознавания речи.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a54a0-104">Emulation is the process by which text, instead of audio, is the input to a speech recognition engine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a54a0-105">Для обхода аудио входы для <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> объекта при эмуляции, используйте <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SetInputToNull%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a54a0-105">To bypass the audio inputs for a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object during emulation, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SetInputToNull%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a54a0-106">Если модуль распознавания речи возникает исключение во время операции распознавания <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> свойству исключение и <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> свойству `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a54a0-106">If the speech recognition engine encounters an exception during the recognition operation, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> property is set to the exception and the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property is set to `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a54a0-107">Интерфейс <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> является производным от интерфейса <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a54a0-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="a54a0-108">В следующем примере добавляется обработчик событий для <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> событие <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a54a0-108">The following example adds an event handler for the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> event to a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a54a0-109">Обработчик получает распознанный текст из <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> свойство.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a54a0-109">The handler gets the recognized text from the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  
  
// Initialize the speech recognition engine.   
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  
  // Add a handler for the EmulateRecognizeCompleted event.  
  sre.EmulateRecognizeCompleted += new EventHandler<EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs>(sre_EmulateRecognizeCompleted);  
  
  // Add other initialization code here.  
}  
  
// Handle the EmulateRecognizeCompleted event.   
void sre_EmulateRecognizeCompleted(object sender, EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs e)  
{  
  if (e.Result == null) return;  
  
  string phrase = e.Result.Text;  
  
  // Add event handler code here.  
}  
  
```
